            <lg xml:id="TK39">
<l>aṟattāṉ varuvatē yiṉpamaṟ ṟellām</l>
<l>puṟatta pukaḻu mila</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Only that pleasure which flows from domestic virtue is pleasure; all else is not pleasure, and it is without praise.</l>
